title: The Morning After The First Playoff Win
itunes:title: The Morning After The First Playoff Win
description: It's the morning after the first playoff win! Kelly is back in the studio in great spirits after the Rams won big in the playoffs. Kelly talks about the game & her nerves, some funny stories about the kids, a story about her & Matthew at the Sugar Bowl & answers a few listener questions.The Morning After podcast is produced by ACTIONPARK MEDIA. Follow us on Social Media:@actionparkmediagroup @kbstafford89@themorningafter.kellystafford
